<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HKMC | Kerala's Lifesteal Network</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;500;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script> <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #ff1a1a; /* Hardcore Red */
            --dark: #0f0f0f;
            --card-bg: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.6);
            --glass: 10px;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #050505;
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, #3a0000 0%, transparent 50%),
                url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/dark-matter.png');
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            height: 80vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .logo-img {
            width: 180px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5));
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin: 10px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            background: -webkit-linear-gradient(#fff, #ff4d4d);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .server-ip {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        
        .server-ip:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--primary);
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* Features Grid (Cards) */
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 50px 10%;
            margin-top: -100px; /* Overlap effect */
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(var(--glass));
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(var(--glass));
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            transition: 0.4s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .card h3 {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .card p {
            color: #ccc;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Live Status Badge */
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.2);
            color: #4dff4d;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #4dff4d;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="hero">
        <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="HKMC Logo" class="logo-img">
        
        <div class="status-badge">
            ‚óè <%= online ? 'Server Online' : 'Server Offline' %>
        </div>

        <h1>Hardcore Kerala<br>Minecraft Community</h1>
        <p style="color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 30px;">The Ultimate Lifesteal SMP Experience</p>

        <div class="server-ip" onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText('play.hkmc.fun'); alert('IP Copied!');">
            play.hkmc.fun <span style="font-size:0.8em; opacity:0.7;">(Click to Copy)</span>
        </div>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9rem;">
            Currently Playing: <strong><%= players %> / <%= max %></strong>
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
        
        <div class="card">
            <h3>‚ö° 24/7 Uptime</h3>
            <p>We use high-performance Ryzens nodes hosted in Mumbai. Low ping for Kerala players and zero downtime ensured.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>üõ°Ô∏è Active Staff</h3>
            <p>Our staff team is active round the clock to keep the server fair. No hackers, no abuse, just pure skill-based gameplay.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>‚ù§Ô∏è Lifesteal Mechanics</h3>
            <p>Kill players to steal their hearts. Lose all hearts and get banned. The stakes have never been higher.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="border-color: #ffd700;">
            <h3 style="color: #ffd700;">üëë Top Killer</h3>
            <% if(leaderboard.length > 0) { %>
                <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: bold;"><%= leaderboard[0].username %></p>
                <p>Kills: <%= leaderboard[0].kills %> | Hearts: <%= leaderboard[0].hearts %></p>
            <% } else { %>
                <p>No data yet.</p>
            <% } %>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
